OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLenders cut mortgage rates 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto ease borrowers' pain    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Mortgage lenders have started the year 
OL,6, by cutting rates, taking some of the   
OL,7, pain out of the cost of a new deal for 
OL,8, homeowners.                            
OL,10,FThe UK's biggest lender, the Halifax,  
OL,11,Fhas cut some interest rates by close to
OL,12,Fone percentage point, with brokers now 
OL,13,Fexpecting others to follow suit.       
OL,15,FHSBC has announced it will make cuts on
OL,16,FThursday, in what is being described as
OL,17,Fa "fast-moving market".                
OL,19,FBut homeowners are being warned to pay 
OL,20,Fclose attention to what is offered.    
